final String companyMessage = 'Medilance is a Pharmaceutical Company in Chandigarh that deals in PCD Pharma Franchise Business & pharma manufacturing. We are rapidly heading to the success in the pharmaceutical industry. All this became possible only because of our true commitment towards the quality of pharmaceutical products and our deep dedication and commitment towards the quality delivery of products. Over the next decade, our aim is to transform the organisation to an innovative company with an innovative portfolio of the business. Our objective will also be to build global leadership position across all therapeutic areas. As we move towards the next altitude of growth and sustainability, I thank you for backing us at every stage and seek your support and guidance in our endeavour. I would like to express my sincere gratitude to one and all for their co-operation and continued support.';